Task 1 – Mobile App Signup Flow

This UI/UX task includes the design of a mobile app signup flow using Figma.

Screens Designed:
- Welcome Screen
- Signup Screen
- Login Screen
- Social Login Options (Google, Facebook, Instagram)

Tools Used:
- Figma (for design and prototype)

Files Included:
- PNG/JPG screenshots of each screen
- `.fig` source file (optional)

Navigation Flow:
User lands on Welcome screen → Clicks “Get Started” → Opens Signup Screen → Can switch to Login → Login via Email or Social Networks.

## Figma Design
[View the Glow Up Email Template on Figma](https://www.figma.com/design/7wm6Il7atb69VWA6dNAKO0/Untitled?node-id=4-2&t=DcogYt4uWfPhbD2N-1)
